properties.property: Welcome! Begin your quest to the SANDWICH MAN. Press your LEFT AND RIGHT arrow keys to move!
Press SPACE to jump! Cross this body of water to continue! Collect Coins on the way for your sandwich!

You made it! But it looks like a lever needs to be pulled... Press SPACE while in the air for a double jump. Press an arrow key beforehand for a dive! Use your newfound knowledge to find a way forward.
This is the lever! What is that down there and slightly to the right though? It looks dangerous... like an enemy. Maybe don't touch that.
